ill better constrain galaxy formation and perhaps also\ncosmological parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jun 2007 09:06:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2007 16:58:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
